{
  "text": "Service to others that have potentiated that which is not. Could you expand that a little bit so I can understand it better? If you see the energy centers in their various colors completing the spectrum, you may see that the service to others choice is one which denies the very center of the spectrum that being universal love. Therefore, all that is built upon the penetration of the light of harvestable equality by such entities is based upon an omission. This omission shall manifest in a fourth density as the love of a self that is the fullest expression of the orange and a yellow energy centers which then are used to potentiate communication and adepthood. When a fifth of density, a refinement has been achieved, that which is not is carried further, the wisdom, a density, a being explored by entities which have no compassion and no universal love. They experience that which they wish by free choice, a being of the earnest opinion that green ray energy is folly. That which is not may be seen as a self-imposed darkness in which harmony is turned into an eternal disharmony. However, that which is not cannot endure throughout the octave of third density, and as darkness eventually calls the light, so does that which is not eventually call that which is a little bit more.",
